query:
INSERT INTO user_progress (userId, courseId, topicId, status, score, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT 7, 30002, t.id, 'in_progress', 0, NOW(), NOW()
FROM topics t
WHERE t.courseId = 30002
  AND NOT EXISTS (
    SELECT 1 FROM user_progress up 
    WHERE up.userId = 7 AND up.topicId = t.id
  );
